To install the openSUSE bento theme, do this: 

cd <wikidir>
sudo git clone git://gitorious.org/opensuse/webdesign.git
cd skins
sudo ln -s ../webdesign/design_concept/theme_o.o-bento-mediawiki/bento bento
sudo ln -s ../webdesign/design_concept/theme_o.o-bento-mediawiki/bento.deps.php
sudo ln -s ../webdesign/design_concept/theme_o.o-bento-mediawiki/bento.php

